MECHANICS' LIEN
NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN THAT: Pursuant to the provisions of the Nevada
Statutes, Radco Construction, LLC, 670 Professional Avenue, #403, Henderson, NV
89015 hereafter referred to as "Claimant" (whether singular or plural), claims a lien
upon the real property and buildings, improvement or structures thereon, described in
Paragraph Six (6)below, and states the following:
(1a) The amount of the original contract is $592,671.50
(1b) The total amount of additional or changed work, materials and equipment if any
is $592,671.50
(1c) The total amount of all payments received to date is $310,700.20
(1d)
That demand of Claimant after deducting all just credits and offsets is
$282,007.31 together with interest thereon at the rate of 18.00 percent per month
from July 8, 2020:
(2) That the name of the owner(s) or reputed owner(s) of said property, is (are):
Ralph V. Franco and Cristeta Franco, 5300 East Agio Avenue, Pahrump, NV 89061.
(3) That Claimant did from October 16, 2019 until July 7, 2020 perform labor
and/or supply materials as follows: All labor and materials. for construction,
alteration or repair of said building, improvements or structures, which labor, or
materials, or both of them were in fact used in the construction, alteration or repair of
said buildings, improvements or structures, the location of which is set forth in
Paragraph Six (6) below.
Construction Notice Services, Inc. (76467)
